.section_box {

/* Top Buy */
.top_buy {
    position: absolute;
    top: 100px;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 999;
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
}

.top_buy .top_content {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 13px 0;
}

.top_buy .top_content p {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 20px;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin: 0;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth span {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin-right: 40px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth span:hover {
    cursor: pointer;
    color: #D2D2D7;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth span.active {
    color: #D2D2D7;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth .buy_button>a {
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #000000;
    padding: 5px 20px;
    background: #03F2A6;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 40px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth .buy_button>a:hover {
    background: #00cc88;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth .buy_button:hover .shop_popup {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth .shop_popup {
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: 30px;
    padding-top: 30px;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth .popup_box {
    width: 165px;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 0 10px;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth .popup_box a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 14px;
    color: #747476;
    padding: 5px 0;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth .popup_box a img {
    max-width: 26px;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth .popup_box a:nth-child(1) {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #D2D2D7;
}

.top_buy .top_content .rigth .popup_box a:hover {
    color: #000000;
}

.top_50 {
